Description:
Handmade/ handwoven gentleman’s travel leather wash bag with compartments to organise bathroom grooming essentials and toiletries in two elastic bands, large mesh pouch for frequently used long toiletries (toothpaste, toothbrush, electric razor (includes six sections 2-5cm width). Includes:
- 1 horizontal elastic holders, 1 clear inner plastic bag liquids/bottles etc. - easy airport security scan;
- Exterior: Mantidy signature herringbone full-grain cowhide leather, vegetable tanned;
- High-quality, fine and durable water-resistant 100% cotton fabric.
